{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2020/11/frontend-dynamic-plugin-implement/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0df3fc9c-5f5d-5cce-8aac-98d2b8da996e","html":"<p>如何在前端动态安装、运行插件？之前一直好奇这个问题，正巧最近看到一篇文章《<a href=\"https://dzone.com/articles/dynamically-pluggable-frontend-architecture\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Creating a Frontend Architecture With Dynamic Plugins</a>》，于是我参照大体思路，用 Apollo &#x26; React 做一个<a href=\"https://github.com/BerlinChan/frontend-dynamic-plugin-demo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">实现 Demo</a>。</p>\n<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<h2 id=\"demo-repository\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#demo-repository\" aria-label=\"demo repository permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Demo Repository</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/BerlinChan/frontend-dynamic-plugin-demo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">frontend-dynamic-plugin-demo</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"思路\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF\" aria-label=\"思路 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>思路</h2>\n<p>前端动态加载插件，最小化情况的关键两点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>获取已安装插件的列表，按照插件的 metadata 信息，<strong>显示插件模块入口</strong>。入口可以是导航菜单、Tab页、按钮等。</li>\n<li><strong>加载并运行</strong>插件入口 js 文件。入口文件运行后，可以是将插件内容渲染进核心程序界面预留的标签中，或弹出 Modal窗口等。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"更多考虑\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E8%80%83%E8%99%91\" aria-label=\"更多考虑 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>更多考虑</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>真实情况中，已安装插件的信息肯定是在数据库中维护的。本例为简单从文件中读取。</li>\n<li>在大型项目中，需要为插件开发提供便于调试的环境，和打包插件的构建程序。</li>\n<li>核心程序与插件、插件与插件之间的通讯，可以用抽象出的 store 实现。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>还有更多复杂场景，在参照的文章作者写的第二篇 <a href=\"https://dzone.com/articles/scale-your-frontend-application-dynamically\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Scale Your Frontend Application</a> 中讨论了很多。</p>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://dzone.com/articles/dynamically-pluggable-frontend-architecture\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Creating a Frontend Architecture With Dynamic Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dzone.com/articles/scale-your-frontend-application-dynamically\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Scale Your Frontend Application</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"如何在前端动态安装、运行插件？之前一直好奇这个问题，正巧最近看到一篇文章《Creating a Frontend Architecture With Dynamic Plugins》，于是我参照大体思路，用 Apollo & React 做一个实现 Demo。","fields":{"slug":"/2020/11/frontend-dynamic-plugin-implement","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"],"tagSlugs":["/tag/apollo/","/tag/react/","/tag/插件/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"前端动态插件的实现 with Apollo & React","date":"2020-11-24T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["前端"],"description":null,"tags":["Apollo","React","插件"],"slug":"/2020/11/frontend-dynamic-plugin-implement","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c31ea7093e30e6ec6bb701dc6b4db911/e737e/alternative-energy-1042411_1280.jpg","srcSet":"/static/c31ea7093e30e6ec6bb701dc6b4db911/e737e/alternative-energy-1042411_1280.jpg 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/c31ea7093e30e6ec6bb701dc6b4db911/e7773/alternative-energy-1042411_1280.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}}}},"prevPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/11/read-listen-to-music-2"},"frontmatter":{"title":"《聆听音乐》读书笔记（二、三）"}},"nextPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021/03/Scaling-to-1-million-active-GraphQL-subscriptions"},"frontmatter":{"title":"借助 GraphQL 承载 100万并发活动订阅（实时查询）"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020/11/frontend-dynamic-plugin-implement","prevPostSlug":"/2020/11/read-listen-to-music-2","nextPostSlug":"/2021/03/Scaling-to-1-million-active-GraphQL-subscriptions"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}